Have a pre-sale question? Please open a sales ticket 24/7 by visiting our website at https://www.meanservers.com or our live chat feature during normal business hours. We try and answer questions on this thread but keep in mind, it is off site and therefore, a low priority. If you have an urgent question, please use our official channels instead.

We are located in the Viawest data center in the heart of downtown Denver, Colorado with excellent speeds and latency to every corner of the country and globe! We own all of our own equipment and have offices in the same building as our data center.

Mean Servers is assigned IP addresses directly from ARIN, not our upstream providers like other hosts. Check out our network, our speeds are blazing fast! All of our nodes are on dual 1Gbps bonded ports to our routers with quad 1Gbps drops from ViaWest, take a look with our &lt;a href="https://www.meanservers.com/looking-glass.php"&gt;looking glass just to see how amazing our network is&lt;/a&gt;. We also are dual stacked supporting both IPv4 and IPv6 natively, no tunnels here! rDNS entries are made straight through our SolusVM control panel, no need to open a ticket like with other hosts!

Every Linux 1GB LET Special VPS Plan we sell includes a free DirectAdmin license for the life of the service you have with Mean Servers. All of our servers boast the newest generation of components made by leading brands such as Dell and HP. Mean Servers NEVER oversells and keeps a cloud platform making it easy to move your VPS to a new node if you wish to upgrade your plan. Every VPS plan also includes access to our SolusVM VPS Control Panel allowing our clients to reboot, shutdown, VNC, change root passwords, and reload the operating system without intervention from us. All of our VPS plans utilize KVM technology giving you privacy, speed, guaranteed resources, and root access.

